##DESCRIPTION
## Simple Interest: Compute Intrest made on stock investment
##ENDDESCRIPTION

##KEYWORDS('financial mathematics', 'simple interest')

## DBsubject('Financial Mathematics')
## DBchapter('Introduction to Interest')
